Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 一個人都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是突發奇想 但真是個好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲了我好幾隻腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 別那麼生氣嘛 小八
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八的腳腳還能再長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是好法子咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在我面前哼你那煩人的饒舌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這廢材蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是養著你的我 最清楚的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別又想出什麼餿主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我終於擺脫大哥的管束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了村子 獲得自由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家現在都以為我被曉抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影現在肯定大發雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我身為人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直作為村子的軍力被束縛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也需要透透氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到演歌的話 就數阿三老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住了 笨蛋 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是演歌忍者的首領啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真夠悠哉的 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉可不會對你不聞不問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且把我召喚出來 你也沒剩多少體力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你既然佔了上風 為何還召我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 與我交手的敵人中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個寫輪眼可算數一數二的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就玩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來時代差不多要改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的演歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空間忍術 還真是個棘手的術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師 那傢伙所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易相信那傢伙的話很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那傢伙所言屬實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但衝動是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑所說的事目前作為我們之間的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是極秘事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直村子復興之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡量避免引起不必要的混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那番話在未經查證之前也不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬滅了宇智波一族是受木葉上層指使等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們尚未知曉的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須佐能乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是萬花筒寫輪眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波…總是隱藏著一些東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶 砂的各位 暫時退避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是這些柱子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柱子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣屋頂會頂不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道團藏所在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重吾和水月怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的查克拉還…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 現在團藏更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 風影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助那傢伙 似乎趁亂逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這慘狀來看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人不知道怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊追蹤佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是往上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然刀因此掉了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 香燐還有重吾怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不簡單 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 團藏跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水影大人跟長十郎留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追團藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會談還沒結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 不過切忌深追
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼曉的賊人就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腰會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們亂來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香燐 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水影大人的血繼限界 熔遁之術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將第四代水影當作玩具差使…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意蹂躪霧隱的曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細瞧瞧 宇智波一族果然都很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你一個蝕骨熔心的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻吻…吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…何方妖孽 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼色誘啊 明明是個老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水影大人…要動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要守護好水影大人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是打敗了再不斬先生的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的人…真的能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我能行…我…會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作行得通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土影大人 你要是不參戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就低頭躲開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來這招嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 低頭躲得開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲆鰈 解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身的細胞都很痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是須佐能乎的副作用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到長時間使用會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒有變成完全體 就已經這麼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬究竟是如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就能獨處了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙被幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的查克拉流動停止了 我還覺得奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你旁邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道牆壁在我剛才攻擊時已經堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 這裡就是徹底的密室了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以使用火 水 土三種性質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的血繼限界有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸遁.巧霧之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那堵牆後面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在溶解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…佐助的查克拉正在減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你在下面被雷影殿下搞得很慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我可不打算放過你 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然每次看到帥哥被熔解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓我覺得心痛不已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是請你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是酸霧嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…剛剛那個曉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒人察覺到孢子之術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五影還真是意外地疏忽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把我的查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸收查克拉然後成長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在被雷影幹掉之前設下的時限式術吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉…在不斷恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸霧正向大家的方向洩露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不改變濃度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來陷入苦戰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤土…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多也該參戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.加重巖之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個小鬼幹掉了迪達拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然跟你無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但忍者們都希望你死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵遁.原界剝離之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的查克拉…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個身軀以近乎分子的狀態被分解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土影 佐助在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我化作塵土了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢擅作主張…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大呼小叫的 雷影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之名 宇智波斑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你們說明一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們理解後 我要聽聽你們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月之眼計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是月之眼計劃的真正目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能將世界交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平只有在現實世界中實現才有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是在逃避而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 交涉失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就在戰場上見了
